name: Windmill and Wyse
description:
This week we'll hit the 'W' streets by first running down Wyse Rd all the way to the smoke stacks and then back up Windmill.
Once we reach the Alderney ferry terminal, we'll head up Octerloney back to the Gazebo.
As always, we meet at the Sullivans Pond Gazebo at 6:30pm.
